body: Object-oriented programming, recursion, fundamental data structures (including stacks, queues, linked lists, hash tables, trees, and graphs), the basics of algorithmic analysis, and an introduction to the principles of language translation.(Credits: 3)(Prerequisites: Prerequisite: CMPSC121)(Additional Attributes: NONE)
